{"tid":1765264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（突登）朝早9點林奠同于品海會出現係港麗！！","createTime":"2019-12-01T17:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T01:32:06.000Z","uid":283870,"like":191,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef3a9ee802589b7614c48a1f541da37b7fe5e71","tid":1765264,"uid":283870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:19:52.000Z","msg":"藍到發紅既香港01！！<br />\n朝早9點既財經高峰會請咗林奠做speaker，老細于品海都會同場出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />～手足得閒記住早啲起身招呼下兩位！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港01財經高峰會<br />\n時間：9點鐘（一開波係于品海同林鄭講辭）<br />\n地點：金鐘港麗酒店大禮堂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅底01多次吹風向出賣手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次仲痴埋林奠，唔好放過佢地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要做野既手足自己早啲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7587f5ca182ce1ec7c649ae5ca99892a2a12ce1c","tid":1765264,"uid":283870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:21:20.000Z","msg":"推啊！！！<br />\n朝早（2號）就係啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f2a55b7bc8290bddf3da3c9896389d4f8a66bc","tid":1765264,"uid":283870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a63a06e7af186326f192aab71a4d221aac61a4","tid":1765264,"uid":155412,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"林奠+于品海呢個組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcd08c59acb02fb9c8dc209490076d48bf53b76","tid":1765264,"uid":283870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4a63a06e7af186326f192aab71a4d221aac61a4","tid":1765264,"uid":155412,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"林奠+于